WEBVTT

00:01:27.447 --> 00:01:33.656
He got tired of looking for answers to these
questions and sat down to meditate.

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:36.490
After a lot of hard work, 
God appeared before him and said,

00:01:36.514 --> 00:01:38.976
“Ask for what you'd like?"

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.976
The man decided to use
the opportunity and said,

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.416
“Dear lord, nothing much,
just give me control,

00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:47.601
so from now onwards things
go the way I want.”

00:01:47.601 --> 00:01:50.424
God said, “Sure, from this moment on 
you are in control,

00:01:50.424 --> 00:01:52.584
what you desire is the way things will be.”

00:01:52.584 --> 00:01:55.770
He was over the moon! He got a car,
a bungalow, air conditioner, TV,

00:01:55.770 --> 00:01:58.566
and ordered whatever he needed
to make himself comfortable.

00:01:58.566 --> 00:02:00.946
He kept getting all the things he desired.